Class NaturalPersonEntrepreneur2

  • java.lang.Object
    • sample.Persons.NaturalPersonEntrepreneur2
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class NaturalPersonEntrepreneur2
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    It is a class which represents a user - natural person-entrepreneur of type 2.
    It contains some common information like Name, Location, BirthYear, IdentificationCode.
    It also has all essential information about the user, on which all the taxes are based, and its taxes.
    And as it's an application, the class contains also user's login and password for access control.
    This class also represents Adapter pattern.
